{"tid":2068902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"江蘇男點蚊香用紙盒墊底　忘記內藏15萬元現鈔　意外燒着剩1.2萬","createTime":"2020-06-18T04:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T04:31:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4d8e830e57b654dcc046de56c911d3458dc03e61","tid":2068902,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"江蘇省南通市通州區一名姓李的男子為求「有覺好瞓」，臨睡前點起蚊香放在紙盒上，豈料燒着紙盒，連同盒內逾15萬元人民幣（約16.4萬港元）現鈔也被燒；他其後拿着該批殘缺紙幣往銀行求助，經工作人員點算及鑑定後，最終兌換得1.2萬元人民幣（約1.3萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n李男當晚點起了蚊香放在一個紙盒上，呼呼入睡之際，突然聞到一股刺鼻的煙味驚醒過來，發現紙盒疑被掉下的灼熱蚊香灰點着了燃燒起來；他將火勢撲滅後，才猛然醒覺紙盒內藏有逾15萬元紙幣，可是大部分已燒至焦黑；他形容那一刻「內心涼了一截」，感到非常自責。<br />\n<br />\n李男拿着燒剩的紙幣到南通市建行通州支行求助，工作人員告知，根據規定，兌換殘缺紙幣需要合資格的銀行職員專門進行點算及鑑定，而李男的紙幣「鑑定工作量會很大」，部份尚能辨別票面的紙幣可全額兌換，餘下的只能半額兌換。<br />\n<br />\n經過逾兩小時的點算及鑑定，該批殘缺紙幣共兌換了1.2萬元人民幣，工作人員強調已盡力解決李男的燃眉之急，同時建議民眾家裡盡量少放現金，應及時存入銀行。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，蚊香在「悶燒」（一種相對低溫、沒有火焰的緩慢燃燒）時，火點最高溫度可達攝氏約700至800度，足以引燃蚊帳、棉布、紙張等物品釀成火災，因此點燃蚊香必須注意與可燃物保持距離。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4701170/org/40873a90019703ed7750d969c05faf71.jpg/LijMKsKlm9r6-6rx-GjNcdVTLA2YgHkeHGl15BxpdeQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4701170%2Forg%2F40873a90019703ed7750d969c05faf71.jpg%2FLijMKsKlm9r6-6rx-GjNcdVTLA2YgHkeHGl15BxpdeQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9eaf96cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4701167/org/214b1c6a1219708e1300a9e0d562c838.jpg/oiCBwXlIRNkgp-6Wmo-NX6jw-dcWY_JpeVE9WXlRPVk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4701167%2Forg%2F214b1c6a1219708e1300a9e0d562c838.jpg%2FoiCBwXlIRNkgp-6Wmo-NX6jw-dcWY_JpeVE9WXlRPVk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c890bcc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"499432d7fa7a88fb8408626a5cb9af8ae9e398e6","tid":2068902,"uid":53105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"人民幣電子化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b1da346eb53edac83a050e692186d7860a6df8","tid":2068902,"uid":23635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:30:06.000Z","msg":"反正都係廢紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9d10a97e7644b861dfeb0fff8d2fb6e29c9e6a","tid":2068902,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:30:07.000Z","msg":"用電子冥幣咪冇事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e837b873851ef9f447eebc095a5c1c267693a0e0","tid":2068902,"uid":185656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:30:56.000Z","msg":"當燒定畀自己囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e4e76b0294f4cb33732285a92b64652eaccce8","tid":2068902,"uid":81424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:31:10.000Z","msg":"專登煲呢啲風險等你班人用電子貨幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022575193cd440eba0072ce969572987c8252b57","tid":2068902,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:31:19.000Z","msg":"留返死左用囉支那狗"}]}